title: Gay Babe | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 27
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


THE BABES are celebrating Pride Month! WELCOME TO GAY BABE! The 10 steps to becoming GAY. The babes finally get to Chris Distefano's David Blaine story!!! SAL IS A DAVID BLAINE FAN GIRL. Shout out magic! Sal has a really embarrassing message he DM'd to David Blaine.....Sal also admits that he's been keeping a journal since the early 1990s. We explore Sal's life through his journal entires GAY BABE! Chris can not believe the DM's Sal sent to David Blaine. What's the gayest food? Sal got a really weird email. Chris talks about the time he got Catfished.....Sal talks about a past AOL based romance he had. SHOUT OUT TOM BRADY! GAY BABE!


Rate us on iTunes!
